snippet.title: The Colossus Is Coming: The Interactive Experience | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The Colossus Is Coming: The Interactive Experience is an upcoming project from FYRE Games, the creators of Summerland, and musical group Auric Echoes.  Experience the Auric Echoes newest album in a whole new way through this beautiful yet haunting experience.

Play The Colossus Is Coming: The Interactive Experience for free on Steam and itch.io December 2, 2020.

Learn more at our website: https://www.fyregames.com/

FYRE Games Instagram: https://instagram.com/fyre_games_offi...
FYRE Games Twitter: https://mobile.twitter.com/fyregamesr...
